---

# Run local preview (Vite)

npm run dev -- --host 127.0.0.1 --port 4173

Open: http://127.0.0.1:4173/

Do not use VS Code "Live Preview" or open index.html directly.
This project uses TypeScript entry files that must be served by Vite.

---

# Build + preview production output

npm run build
npm run preview -- --host 127.0.0.1 --port 4173

---

# Commit + push

git add .
git commit -m "new repo after delete"
git push

---

Use one repo per machine; always git pull before editing, git commit + git push after.
